							Welcome to PR Wave, a dynamic social media marketing agency founded in 2022, 
							successfully serving Georgian businesses. PR Wave is an agency created by 
							Nino Chkheize, a film director and businessman, and Leila Berzenishvili-Qahveji, 
							a financist and digital marketer.
						</p>
						<p data-translate="about.storyPara2">
							At PR Wave, we believe that success is easily achieved through mutual cooperation 
							and innovation implementation. Our unique approach combines the founders' experience 
							with fresh perspectives from young, talented interns. This collaboration allows us 
							to serve clients according to the latest social media trends, delivering real results.
						</p>
